description: List exclusions that are generated by the assessment run.

parameters.name: assessmentRunArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the assessment run that generated the exclusions that you want to list.

nested_items.name: exclusionArns
nested_items.description: A list of exclusions' ARNs returned by the action.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: When a response is generated, if there is more data to be listed, this parameters is present in the response and contains the value to use for the nextToken parameter in a subsequent pagination request. If there is no more data to be listed, this parameter is set to null.
